Titolo: The Adventures of Captain Comic

Anno: 1988

Descrizione: The Adventures of Captain Comic is a platform game written by Michal Denio for MS-DOS and released as shareware in 1988. It was one of the first side-scrolling games for IBM PC compatibles reminiscent of games for the Nintendo Entertainment System, and it presaged a trend of shareware platform games in the early 1990s. A version for the NES was later published by Color Dreams as an unlicensed title.